            <scopecontent id="aspace_c30caef79354d95781a3218068dc59d3">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The Viscount James Bryce Papers consist of two signed manuscripts, the second and third of three articles by Bryce, which appeared under the title "Impressions of South Africa" in the <title render="italic">
                     <part>Century Illustrated Monthly Magazine</part>
                  </title>, May-July, 1896. Bryce reprinted the articles in 1897 as a book by the same title.</p>
            </scopecontent>
